languages.text: "Может быть... они здесь не для того, чтобы вредить нам? Насколько я знаю, агрокомплексы работают, поставки отправляются. Жизнь... словно идет как шла до этого".

languages.text: "Maybe... they're not here to hurt us? As far as I know, the agri-complexes are running, supplies are being shipped out. Life is... just as it was before."

languages.text: “或许……他们并不是来伤害我们的？据我所知，综合农业中心依然在正常运转，物资也依然在正常运输。生活……就和以前一样。”

languages.text: «¿Y si... no están aquí para hacernos daño? Por lo que tengo entendido, los complejos agrícolas funcionan y los suministros se envían. Las cosas... han vuelto a la normalidad».
languages.original_text: "Maybe... they're not here to hurt us? As far as I know, the agri-complexes are running, supplies are being shipped out. Life is... just as it was before."

languages.text: 「たぶん…彼らは私達を傷つけに来たわけではないのかな？知る限りだけど、農業複合施設は動いてるし、食糧は出荷されてる。暮らしは…以前と何ら変わらない」
languages.original_text: "Maybe... they're not here to hurt us? As far as I know, the agri-complexes are running, supplies are being shipped out. Life is... just as it was before."

traits.locale_text: 「たぶん…彼らは私達を傷つけに来たわけではないのかな？知る限りだけど、農業複合施設は動いてるし、食糧は出荷されてる。暮らしは…以前と何ら変わらない」

languages.text: "Vielleicht ... wollen sie uns gar nicht schaden? Soweit ich weiß, laufen die Agri-Komplexe und die Vorratslieferungen. Das Leben ist ... wieder so wie zuvor."
languages.original_text: "Maybe... they're not here to hurt us? As far as I know, the agri-complexes are running, supplies are being shipped out. Life is... just as it was before."

languages.text: « Peut-être... qu'ils ne nous veulent aucun mal ? D'après ce que je sais, les agri-complexes fonctionnent comme d'habitude et les convois de marchandises circulent normalement. Finalement, la vie... suit son cours. »
